{"tid":754552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蝗蟲過境] 赴日打針攻略殺到！ 網傳日本曾捐疫苗","createTime":"2018-07-24T13:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T00:54:42.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f280b40ce3febfd4bffa57e62683fb636fb3ea0","tid":754552,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"中國假疫苗風波愈演愈烈，謠言四起。內地網民就假疫苗的新聞與未經證實的傳言也滿天飛，有網民昨日（23日）宣稱，中國早年使用的防疫疫苗全是日本捐贈的，但隨後有人駁斥說，這並非完整事實，日本確實有捐疫苗，但不是「所有人體內都是日本疫苗」。另外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有網民則貼出到日本注射疫苗的詳細攻略，指日本政府准許外國人到日本注射疫苗，如果沒錢還可以申請減免，只需提前預約即可</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在微博發帖寫道，日本在1980、90年代透過聯合國向中國捐贈所有疫苗，直到2008年才停止援助，現在所有「80後」「90後」的青年，體內都有日本疫苗，而中國官方從未對民眾公開這件事，還有傳言說，中國當局在已在微博封鎖「日本捐贈疫苗」的討論。<br />\n但實際在微博搜索，仍可看到不少相關討論，有網民指稱，「所有人都打過日本疫苗」，並非全然事實，網友說根據記錄顯示，日本多年前曾捐贈小兒痲痺疫苗、結核病疫苗，日本還派專家到中國協助培訓相關技術，提供器材等，但目前沒看到證據顯示「80、90年代的疫苗都來自日本」。另有網民進一步解釋：「古巴單單1999年就向中國捐贈115萬美元乙肝疫苗；另外，中國也向印度、敍利亞、非洲捐贈疫苗，怎麼不提？」<br />\n內地網民赴日打針攻略詳細解釋流程、疫苗價格，指在網上預約好日本醫院，不懂日語可盡量找英語醫生，還能預約東京當地的國際醫院。以「百白破」三合一疫苗的價格為7,000日圓（約474港元），而日本厚生勞動省規定，即使沒有居留資格的外國人，也可以接受定期的預防疫苗接種，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而中國旅客只要辦理旅遊簽證就行，幾千元人民幣機票，就能讓孩子在日本接種疫苗帶來保障。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180724/58481879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F58481879&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8c71f67a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F58481879&h=f8d2af73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180724/58481879</a>"},{"pid":"348f589969f8e20bc5db7070bd2a00416effe6c6","tid":754552,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"支那人滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb22a1685bbfb63ee7a50124a93f21d26876696","tid":754552,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf77ec36d8aa1b929229c30a2a1ed80bfec987e","tid":754552,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:27:05.000Z","msg":"日本rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb14fc25f62a1f899aa04a6d0a81f5685f6d73cd","tid":754552,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e50616e0c24e2ae6a5eecba1dd2b038a3edce3","tid":754552,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:28:27.000Z","msg":"蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19855162b56cdf5a4ac100f4fe09abddf9499d73","tid":754552,"uid":126283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"愛国不用小日本疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134004cbb10b800f6443561d5494b38223408929","tid":754552,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"口裏說不"},{"pid":"c9b0bc32f7f2e1e29322a7dfbb9e2791fc213500","tid":754552,"uid":68080,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古巴單單1999年就向中國捐贈115萬美元乙肝疫苗；另外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國也向印度、敍利亞、非洲捐贈疫苗</span></span>，怎麼不提？」<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來害埋印度、敘利亞同埋非洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98394e02e9935d9a34407de975e2acdbb258bf37","tid":754552,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci